data.description: Located in exclusive Jacaranda Country Club and situated on the golf course. Room to roam in this over 3,100 SQ FT pool home. Updated eat-in kitchen with granite counters, center island and ample cabinet space. Formal living area, separate dining room and informal living area with cathedral ceiling. Huge master suite overlooks pool and golf course. 2 car garage. Come make this home your own. Neighborhood is simply gorgeous and quiet! Located close to I-595 and shopping/restaurants.
